<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='980904' id='t-980904'>think about what you've thought of them,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='982856' id='t-982856'>and then actually do it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='984045' id='t-984045'>because it's something
that's really going to change our lives.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='987067' id='t-987067'>So, thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='988253' id='t-988253'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
